{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"誓以有宫分的苍穹，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"和所警告的日子，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"以及能证的和所证的日子，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"愿掘坑的人们，被弃绝，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"那坑里有燃料点着的火，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"当时，他们坐在坑边，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"他们见证自己对信士们的罪行，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他们对于信士们，只责备他们信仰安拉——万能的，可颂的主，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"天地的主权只是他的，安拉是见证万物的。"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"迫害信士和信女而不悔过的人们，必受火狱的刑罚，并受火灾的惩治。"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"信道而且行善的人们，必入下临诸河的乐园，那确是伟大的成功。"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"你的主的惩治，确是严厉的。"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"他确能创造，且能再造，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"他是至赦的，是至爱的，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"是宝座的主，是尊严的，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"是为所欲为的。"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"你曾听见军队的故事了吗？"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"法老和赛莫德人的故事。"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"不然，不信道的人们陷于否认之中，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"安拉是从各方面包罗他们的，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"不然，这是尊严的《古兰经》，"},{"SurahNumber":85,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"记录在一块受保护的天牌上。"}]}